{"ok":true,"module":"poollogic/sensors","docs":{"poollogic/sensors/air_temp_io_id":{"type":"UInt16","label_t":"cfgdocs.poollogic.sensors.air_temp_io_id.label","help_t":"cfgdocs.poollogic.sensors.air_temp_io_id.help","enum_set":"flowio_logical_input_analog","label":"IO température air","label_i18n":"cfgdocs.poollogic.sensors.air_temp_io_id.label","help":"Identifiant IO de la sonde température air.","help_i18n":"cfgdocs.poollogic.sensors.air_temp_io_id.help"},"poollogic/sensors/chl_lvl_io_id":{"type":"UInt16","label_t":"cfgdocs.poollogic.sensors.chl_lvl_io_id.label","help_t":"cfgdocs.poollogic.sensors.chl_lvl_io_id.help","enum_set":"flowio_logical_input_digital","label":"IO niveau cuve chlore","label_i18n":"cfgdocs.poollogic.sensors.chl_lvl_io_id.label","help":"Identifiant IO de l'entrée digitale niveau bas cuve chlore.","help_i18n":"cfgdocs.poollogic.sensors.chl_lvl_io_id.help"},"poollogic/sensors/filtr_fb_io_id":{"type":"UInt16","label_t":"cfgdocs.poollogic.sensors.filtr_fb_io_id.label","help_t":"cfgdocs.poollogic.sensors.filtr_fb_io_id.help","enum_set":"flowio_logical_input_digital","label":"IO retour contacteur filtration","label_i18n":"cfgdocs.poollogic.sensors.filtr_fb_io_id.label","help":"Entree logique du retour auxiliaire du contacteur de filtration. Par defaut: i04 sur GPIO8.","help_i18n":"cfgdocs.poollogic.sensors.filtr_fb_io_id.help"},"poollogic/sensors/filtr_fb_mon":{"type":"Bool","label_t":"cfgdocs.poollogic.sensors.filtr_fb_mon.label","help_t":"cfgdocs.poollogic.sensors.filtr_fb_mon.help","label":"Surveillance contacteur filtration","label_i18n":"cfgdocs.poollogic.sensors.filtr_fb_mon.label","help":"Compare la commande du relais de filtration avec son contact auxiliaire. Un ecart de 5 secondes declenche une alarme et interdit l'electrolyseur.","help_i18n":"cfgdocs.poollogic.sensors.filtr_fb_mon.help"},"poollogic/sensors/orp_io_id":{"type":"UInt16","label_t":"cfgdocs.poollogic.sensors.orp_io_id.label","help_t":"cfgdocs.poollogic.sensors.orp_io_id.help","